title: David Liebe Hart and Adam Papagan- Public Access
description:
David Liebe Hart is a puppeteer, actor, songwriter, sign painter, musicainist, and street entertainer from Los Angeles.  He is best know for his long running public access show, performing outside the Hollywood Bowl, and his appearances on The Tim and Eric Great Show Great Job.  This album was recorded in early 2008 with the help of producer Adam Papagan and chronicles David&rsquo;s experiences with women, UFO&rsquo;s, and trying to make it in the entertainment industry.
